WEBVTT

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:11.591
HI, MY NAME IS MAHLI LIEBLICH.

00:01:11.591 --> 00:01:15.691
TODAY I AM INTERVIEWING MISTER JOSEF KATZ.

00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:23.140
WE ARE IN MIAMI BEACH, FLORIDA, UNITED STATES OF AMERICA. IT IS MARCH TWENTY SEVENTH, NINETEEN NINETY SIX.

00:01:23.140 --> 00:01:25.166
AND THIS IS TAPE NUMBER ONE.

00:01:28.980 --> 00:01:30.410
vos iz dayn nomen?

00:01:30.430 --> 00:01:32.850
mayn nomen iz Yosef Kats.

00:01:32.930 --> 00:01:36.900
AND vos iz dayn nomen, ven du host geboyrn gevorn, gevezn?

00:01:37.214 --> 00:01:39.021
Yosef Berger.

00:01:39.330 --> 00:01:43.920
AND far vos iz dayn nomen haynt Kats AND se hot gevezn Berger?

00:01:43.970 --> 00:01:47.883
dos iz, mayn mames nomen iz Kats, un nokhn krig

00:01:48.242 --> 00:01:50.886
hob ikh genumen dem nomen fun Kats.

00:01:51.501 --> 00:01:54.620
vos hot gevezn di nomen fun dayn foter?

00:01:54.987 --> 00:01:57.210
Zalmen-Leyb Berger.

00:01:57.350 --> 00:01:59.470
AND dayn muters nomen?

00:01:59.639 --> 00:02:02.790
iz gevezn Ester Kats.

00:02:03.058 --> 00:02:05.610
velkhe shtot hostu geboyrn gevorn?

00:02:05.690 --> 00:02:08.510
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn in Satmer.

00:02:08.540 --> 00:02:12.010
AND velkhe COUNTRY iz Satmer?

00:02:11.910 --> 00:02:14.618
demolts iz es gevezn in Rumenyen.

00:02:15.462 --> 00:02:17.673
AND du host gehat brider un shvester?

00:02:17.591 --> 00:02:23.981
yo, undz ze'mir gevezn fir briders, un finef shvesters hob ikh gehat.

00:02:24.081 --> 00:02:30.499
fun di eltste biz di yingste, kenst mir zogn di, nomen fun ale briders un shvesters?

00:02:29.320 --> 00:02:29.818
yo.

00:02:30.477 --> 00:02:34.300
di elteste bruder hot geheysn Avrom-Hersh.

00:02:34.470 --> 00:02:38.980
un dan iz gevezn, di eltere shvester iz,

00:02:39.090 --> 00:02:40.580
zi heyst Khane.

00:02:41.805 --> 00:02:45.602
dan bin ikh gekumen, vos ikh heys Yosef,

00:02:45.931 --> 00:02:49.340
un mayn yingerer bruder heyst Sokher-Ber,

00:02:50.112 --> 00:02:53.882
un dan iz gevezn a bruder vos er hot geheysn Shmuel-Osher,

00:02:54.557 --> 00:02:59.078
un dan ho'mir gehat a shvester vos zi hot geheysn Hinde,

00:02:59.705 --> 00:03:06.117
un dan ho'mir gehat a shvester vos zi hot geheysn Golde-Rokhl,

00:03:06.235 --> 00:03:10.000
un di letste shvester hot geheysn Leye.

00:03:10.783 --> 00:03:13.831
AND velkhe yor, vos iz dayn geburts-tog?

00:03:13.905 --> 00:03:24.210
mayn geburts-tog iz yud beys elel, tar-, tar- pey dalet.

00:03:24.425 --> 00:03:28.915
dos iz oyf ungerish oder oyf goyish

00:03:29.024 --> 00:03:33.201
di draytsete september, nayntsn hundert fir un tsvontsik.

00:03:34.599 --> 00:03:39.671
zog mir fun di tate, vos hot di tate getun far parnose?

00:03:39.657 --> 00:03:44.521
der tate hot gehat an WÄSCHEERZEUGUNG in Satmer,

00:03:44.987 --> 00:03:49.580
mit, tsvontsik-draysik arbayter.

00:03:49.811 --> 00:03:52.853
froyen AND MEN tsuzamen, OR nor f- mener?

00:03:52.182 --> 00:03:58.999
nor nor froyen, nor froyen hobn gearbet. eyn man iz gevezn vos er iz gevezn der tsushnayder.

00:03:59.958 --> 00:04:04.208
AND zey hobn gevezn yidishe froyen, tsi farshidene?

00:04:03.118 --> 00:04:07.152
neyn, s'iz geven yidishe oykh, un s'iz geven kristlekhe oykh,

00:04:07.731 --> 00:04:11.790
ungarishe, rumenishe, farshidns. a fabrik, yo.

00:04:08.003 --> 00:04:08.864
SO azoy...

00:04:09.378 --> 00:04:10.702
s'a fabrik.

00:04:11.876 --> 00:04:13.889
AND vos hot di mame getun?

00:04:13.931 --> 00:04:17.979
di mame hot tsugeholfn in gesheft oykh, un in der heym oykh.

00:04:18.256 --> 00:04:21.903
hot men gehat a meshores in der heym far di, ah,

00:04:18.408 --> 00:04:19.040
s'hot gef-...

