zakhn vos me hot gedarft makhn in der heym, un, azoy iz zi gekumen yedn tog in gesheft oykh, un zi hot dort oykh tsugeholfn.

00:04:29.001 --> 00:04:32.260
vi groys hot di shtub gevezn, in der heym?

00:04:32.198 --> 00:04:33.221
in der heym?

00:04:33.549 --> 00:04:39.357
in der heym hobn mir gehat fir shlof-tsimer,

00:04:39.660 --> 00:04:42.053
un a groys es-tsimer,

00:04:42.839 --> 00:04:44.516
un a kokh.

