ober di mame iz geven a khasideske, yo.

00:06:10.736 --> 00:06:16.410
un azoy ze'mir undz shoyn oyfgevaksn, ven der Satmerer rov iz gekumen oyf Satmer tsu zayn rov,

00:06:16.716 --> 00:06:20.803
ze'mir undz shoyn oyfgevaksn gevorn mer khasidish.

00:06:22.163 --> 00:06:24.484
ven du host gevezn a kind,

