yo.

00:06:59.541 --> 00:07:02.985
un dos hot gevezn di yugnt fun di rumenishe MEN.

00:07:01.489 --> 00:07:03.739
di yugnt fun di rumenishe, yo.

00:07:04.027 --> 00:07:09.857
un du host gehert fun zakhn vos hot geshen OR pasirt in SATU MARE?

00:07:09.857 --> 00:07:12.499
vos hot gevezn ANTI-semetish?

00:07:12.746 --> 00:07:17.636
eygntlekh in SATU MARE iz veynik antisemitishe zakhn gevezn.

00:07:17.636 --> 00:07:23.494
s'mer vos me hot gehert in Rumenye fun Bukovine UND fun di alte rumenishe shtet.

00:07:24.054 --> 00:07:28.774
in Satmer aleyn iz veynik antisemitishe zakhn geven.

00:07:28.802 --> 00:07:32.213
vifl yidn hobn gevoynt in SATU MARE?

00:07:32.122 --> 00:07:35.366
in Satmer hobn gevoynt, farn krig, yo?

00:07:35.204 --> 00:07:35.914
yo.

00:07:35.366 --> 00:07:40.013
hobn gevoynt umgefer draytsn-fertsn toyznt yidn.

00:07:40.356 --> 00:07:44.075
AND di gantse shtot, vifl mentshn hot gevezn?

00:07:43.284 --> 00:07:46.262
di gantse shtot iz geven fuftsik toyznt mentshn.

00:07:46.002 --> 00:07:48.290
SO azoy, tsvontsik protsent

00:07:47.822 --> 00:07:49.016
umgefer, yo.

00:07:48.797 --> 00:07:50.444
hot gevezn yidn.

00:07:49.212 --> 00:07:51.808
epes mer vi tsvontsik protsent, yo.

00:07:51.937 --> 00:07:55.856
di gesheftn AND di BUSINESSES in Satmar,

00:07:55.856 --> 00:07:58.427
es hobn gevezn a sakh fun di yidn?

00:07:58.141 --> 00:08:06.103
meynstns yidn, oyfn gantsn geshefts-plats vu s'iz gevezn in di shtot, iz gevezn

00:08:06.512 --> 00:08:08.814
shabes ales tsugeshpart.

00:08:08.827 --> 00:08:10.755
s'iz nisht gevezn keyn ofene.

00:08:11.170 --> 00:08:14.254
in gantsn iz geven eyn eyntsikes gesheft

00:08:14.464 --> 00:08:16.386
vos iz ofn gevezn,

00:08:17.201 --> 00:08:23.861
vayl der iz gevezn a Neolog, oykh a yid ober er hot gehert tsu di Neologn, vayl bay undz iz gevezn a

00:08:23.893 --> 00:08:26.402
Shtatus-Kvo-gemeynde oykh, yo?

00:08:27.117 --> 00:08:31.603
der eyntsiker vos er iz geven ofn um shabes, vayl s'iz ales geven geshpart.

00:08:33.044 --> 00:08:38.424
un s'iz nokh geven eyn goyish gesheft iz oykh gevezn, der iz oykh geven ofn, der iz ober geven a goy.

00:08:38.110 --> 00:08:45.632
 velkhe gesheft hot es gevezn, di goyishe gesheft, vos hot er gehat in di gesheft, du gedenkst?

00:08:48.971 --> 00:08:50.674
