00:08:51.182 --> 00:08:55.396
fun ale dayn briders un shvesters,

00:08:55.396 --> 00:09:00.182
velkhe bruder un velkhe shvester hostu geglaykht di beste?

00:09:02.076 --> 00:09:09.883
dos ken ikh k-, nisht zogn, az di di beste ho'mir geglaykht dos mezinikl, di kleyn-, dos kleynste, yo, dos klenste meydele.

00:09:10.115 --> 00:09:13.319
dey ho'mir, dey hob ikh geglaykht, ammeyn-

00:09:13.422 --> 00:09:17.077
iz geborn in in nayntsn hundert fertsik, yo?

00:09:17.411 --> 00:09:21.301
iz zi in gantsn alt geven fir yor ven zi iz gekumen oyf Oyshvits.

00:09:21.333 --> 00:09:24.825
dey ho- dey ho'mir, ho'mir ale geglaykht ambestn.

00:09:24.597 --> 00:09:29.240
un fun ale dayn briders un shvesters, vifl lebn nokh?

00:09:29.188 --> 00:09:31.422
eyn bruder, a yingerer bruder,

00:09:31.551 --> 00:09:33.181
er lebt in Yerusholaim.

