un dan hob ikh nokh an eltere shvester un a yingere shvester s-, dey lebn ale in Kvins in Nyu-York.

00:09:40.942 --> 00:09:43.524
un vos hot g- pasirt tsu di andere?

00:09:43.590 --> 00:09:49.098
di andere zenen leyder ale umgekumen in Oyshvits un in di lagers.

00:09:50.228 --> 00:09:52.909
zog mir a bisl fun dayn heym.

