ven s'hot gekumt tsu shabes, vi azoy hot di mame gemakht shabes in shtub?

00:09:53.491 --> 00:09:54.024
yo.

00:09:58.661 --> 00:10:00.690
shabes,

00:10:00.690 --> 00:10:03.819
