00:10:03.819 --> 00:10:07.196
ikh bin gegangen entveder in kheyder oder in di shul.

00:10:07.205 --> 00:10:11.364
ikh bin veynik gevezn in der heym ven me hot gemakht dem shabes.

00:10:09.583 --> 00:10:12.798
