00:10:11.459 --> 00:10:16.786
zikher, me hot gekokht far shabes, s'iz geven a goyte dortn vos zi hot geholfn di ale zakhn makhn.

00:10:16.550 --> 00:10:19.655
vos hot di mame gekokht far shabes, gedenkst?

00:10:19.038 --> 00:10:19.633
yo.

00:10:20.177 --> 00:10:24.062
azoy, fraytik oyf der nakht iz gevezn fish,

00:10:25.386 --> 00:10:27.328
un dan iz geven zup,

