alzo barkhes nokh, yo.

00:10:37.513 --> 00:10:40.046
un shabes mitog iz gevezn

00:10:40.983 --> 00:10:44.308
 oykh a bisl fish, un,

00:10:44.363 --> 00:10:46.073
tsvibl mit eyer,

00:10:46.659 --> 00:10:48.918
tsholnt, mit kugl,

