hot men nisht zeyer gegleybt vos zey hobn ales ertseylt.

00:14:56.698 --> 00:15:01.106
vayl in Ungern ken azoy vos nisht pasirn vos s'hot pasirt in Poyln.

00:15:01.106 --> 00:15:03.747
azoy hot, hobn der oylem gezogt.

00:15:05.255 --> 00:15:10.057
velkhe yor hot di Natsis arayngekumen?

00:15:10.081 --> 00:15:14.816
keyn Ungern zenen zey arayngekumen in nayntsn fir un fertsik.

00:15:15.128 --> 00:15:17.214
merts dem nayntsetn.

00:15:17.605 --> 00:15:19.332
tsu Satmer?

00:15:19.378 --> 00:15:20.718
tsu Budapest.

00:15:20.182 --> 00:15:21.415
tsu Budapest.

00:15:21.031 --> 00:15:21.556
yo.

00:15:21.766 --> 00:15:24.821
un dan hobn zey zikh tseshpreyt in gants Ungern.

00:15:25.819 --> 00:15:29.534
un vos hot geshen in Satmar?

00:15:29.534 --> 00:15:37.319
vos hot geve- gevorn andersh in Satmar azoy dray un fertsik, tsvey un fertsik, s'hot gevezn andershe lebn?

00:15:37.319 --> 00:15:40.172
az di milkhome kumt, tsi du host gefilt epes vet...

00:15:39.851 --> 00:15:46.985
neyn. me hot gefilt, me hot gehat zeyer a sheyn lebn di gantse tsayt. me hot nisht gefilt keyn shum milkhome, m'hot

00:15:46.985 --> 00:15:48.802
s'iz gevezn farshidene

00:15:48.901 --> 00:15:57.943
zakhn, az a yid tor nisht hobn a gesheft, hot men zikh genemen a goy far a nomen, un vos veys ikh, un azolkhike zakhn hot men getun.

00:15:58.126 --> 00:16:03.649
ober zonst hot men gekent makhn gute gesheft un me hot gekent zeyer gut lebn.

00:16:03.806 --> 00:16:08.520
SO vos hot getoysht, vos hot gevorn andersh, in velkhe yor?

00:16:08.366 --> 00:16:12.485
in fir un fertsik ven di daytshn zenen arayngekumen.

00:16:10.949 --> 00:16:13.235
un vos hot pasirt?

00:16:13.128 --> 00:16:18.654
vos hot pasirt ken ikh nisht vayter zogn vayl mikh hobn zey glaykh internirt.

00:16:19.378 --> 00:16:21.163
zog mir fun dos.

00:16:20.712 --> 00:16:21.247
yo.

00:16:21.469 --> 00:16:26.194
azoy, merts dem nayntsetn zenen zey arayngekumen oyf Budapest,

00:16:26.347 --> 00:16:32.305
un ikh bin um um tsen a zeyger, un um tsvelef a zeyger bin ikh ongekumen oyf Budapest.

00:16:31.872 --> 00:16:34.712
du host gegan fun Satmer tsu Budapest...

00:16:33.945 --> 00:16:38.078
nisht fun Buda- ikh bin gevezn oyf shabes bin ikh gevezn in, in Debretsen

00:16:38.432 --> 00:16:44.980
vayl dort, hob ikh gehat khaveyrim un zey hobn mikh gerufn, me hot geshpilt demolts mekhires-yosef.

00:16:44.998 --> 00:16:47.705
aza shpil, vayl s'iz gevezn nokh purim,

00:16:47.803 --> 00:16:49.470
shabes oyf der nakht.

00:16:49.568 --> 00:16:53.941
un fun dort bin ikh geforn oyf, Budapest.

00:16:54.067 --> 00:16:57.269
bin ongekumen um tsvelef a zeyger in Budapest,

00:16:58.099 --> 00:17:01.903
di daytshn zenen shoyn dort geven, zey zenen gekumen um tsen a zeyger.

00:17:02.330 --> 00:17:03.724
un baym tsug

00:17:04.061 --> 00:17:06.620
hobn di ungarishe politsey

00:17:06.954 --> 00:17:11.505
hobn glaykh aropgenemen di yidn vos zenen opgeshtign

00:17:11.865 --> 00:17:13.828
un me hot zey glaykh farhaftet.

00:17:14.033 --> 00:17:16.989
un me hot zey gefirt, azoy vi mikh oykh,

00:17:17.248 --> 00:17:20.123
in MOSONYI gas. dort iz gevezn a

00:17:20.188 --> 00:17:22.749
a TÁBOR, a lager, vu...

00:17:23.127 --> 00:17:25.730
un me hot tsuzamengenemen di mentshn, yo?

00:17:25.637 --> 00:17:28.109
vifl mentshn hobn zey tsuzamengenemen?

00:17:28.160 --> 00:17:34.282
dos veys ikh nisht. ikh veys nor undz ze'mir gekumen dem nekstn tog hot men undz gefirt oyf KISTARCSA.

00:17:34.282 --> 00:17:38.324
un dort ze'mir shoyn, dort ze'mir tsuzamengekumen dray toyznt mentshn.

00:17:38.371 --> 00:17:39.423
ale mener.

00:17:39.464 --> 00:17:42.120
neyn, s'iz geven epes froyen oykh.

00:17:43.131 --> 00:17:44.986
un vos hot pasirt...

00:17:43.603 --> 00:17:45.731
ober meynstns mener, yo.

00:17:45.203 --> 00:17:47.360
yo. vos hot pasirt dortn?

00:17:47.396 --> 00:17:49.806
dort in KISTARCSA

00:17:49.901 --> 00:17:52.724
hobn zey undz gornisht getun.

00:17:52.760 --> 00:17:57.834
di JOINT hot geshikt esn durkh di yidishe gemeynde.

00:17:58.070 --> 00:17:58.901
un

00:18:00.482 --> 00:18:03.545
dort hot men nisht gedarft arbetn oder vos.

00:18:03.948 --> 00:18:09.704
shlofn ze'mir ale oyf der erd, vayl s'iz nisht gevezn keyn betn oder azoy vos, yo.

00:18:10.103 --> 00:18:14.633
un dort ze'mir gevezn ts- a finef vokhn.

00:18:16.561 --> 00:18:20.875
mit undz tsuzamen iz gevezn dortn der Koleshitser rebe.

00:18:21.125 --> 00:18:24.437
er iz gevezn a flikhtling fun Poyln.

00:18:25.562 --> 00:18:28.900
er iz dort mit undz gevezn, un

00:18:28.916 --> 00:18:31.637
ze'mir dort gevezn iber peysekh.

00:18:32.312 --> 00:18:36.100
dem seyder hot der Koleshitser rebe gefirt dortn.

00:18:36.163 --> 00:18:38.217
ale ze'mir gezesn oyf der erd.

00:18:38.986 --> 00:18:43.457
bakumen ho'mir tsu esn fun di yidishe gemeynde peysekhik esn.

00:18:43.465 --> 00:18:46.679
du host gehat matse, du host gehat alts vos du darfst.

00:18:45.455 --> 00:18:51.960
gehat matses, vos me darf, vayl di gemeynde hot nokh ekzistirt, un di gemeynde hot nokh gebrengt tsu esn, yo.

00:18:49.322 --> 00:18:52.010
hot gehat az alts, yo.

00:18:53.132 --> 00:18:56.835
un um nekstn inderfri,

00:18:56.956 --> 00:18:58.260
peysekh,

00:18:59.139 --> 00:19:03.919
hot er, hot er undz ertseylt az er hot zikh gekholemt mit zayn foter,

00:19:04.473 --> 00:19:08.097
zayn foter iz gevezn a groyser rebe in Koleshits,

00:19:08.873 --> 00:19:13.560
un der foter hot im gezogt in kholem, "zolst visn,"

00:19:13.865 --> 00:19:17.719
KISTARCSA hot geheysn dos lager-, dos lagerl vu undz ze'mir geven,

00:19:17.804 --> 00:19:20.921
"zolst visn az KISTARCSA iz a kleyner lager,

00:19:21.033 --> 00:19:23.606
Budapest iz a greserer lager.

00:19:23.872 --> 00:19:26.719
ober gants Ungern iz nokh a greserer lager".

00:19:28.981 --> 00:19:32.034
dos hot er undz ertseylt vos er hot zikh gekholemt.

00:19:32.936 --> 00:19:35.873
un undz ze'mir dort gevezn biz nokh peysekh.

00:19:36.714 --> 00:19:40.415
der Koleshitser rebe hot zikh nisht gevolt opshern di bord,

00:19:40.709 --> 00:19:45.846
biz a tog befor un-, me hot undz avekgefirt keyn BIRKENAU.

00:19:46.161 --> 00:19:50.693
vos hot pasirt di, di tog frier? dem tog?

00:19:50.720 --> 00:19:51.650
ven?

00:19:51.709 --> 00:19:57.089
eyn tog frier, du host geganen tsu BIRKENAU, er hot zikh geshoyrn di bord?

00:19:56.060 --> 00:19:58.400
er hot zikh opgeshoyrn di bord, yo.

00:19:57.936 --> 00:19:58.827
far vos?

00:19:58.844 --> 00:20:01.995
vayl er hot gevust az me firt undz dortn avek.

00:20:02.300 --> 00:20:06.390
me hot gemuzt zikh opshern di bord di gantse tsayt. dos iz gevezn a

00:20:06.463 --> 00:20:10.526
a farordenung az me zol zikh opshern... er hot zikh ober nisht gevolt opshern.

00:20:10.905 --> 00:20:16.003
un er hot gehat di bord biz tsum sof. biz a tog far dem vos me hot undz avekgefirt.

00:20:16.056 --> 00:20:18.595
demolts hot er zikh shoyn yo gelozt opshern.

00:20:19.007 --> 00:20:21.840
vayl er hot shoyn gevust vu me firt undz.

00:20:21.994 --> 00:20:23.207
er hot yo gevust.

00:20:23.052 --> 00:20:25.915
er hot yo gevust, er iz dokh gekumen fun Poyln.

00:20:23.959 --> 00:20:25.231
hostu gevust?

00:20:25.748 --> 00:20:26.087
yo.

00:20:26.087 --> 00:20:27.198
hostu gevust?

00:20:26.890 --> 00:20:28.365
ikh hob nisht gevust.

00:20:28.379 --> 00:20:30.012
AND er hot nisht dir gezogt.

00:20:30.062 --> 00:20:31.854
er hot gezogt,

00:20:32.436 --> 00:20:34.902
ven mir ze'mir geven in tsug hot er shoyn gezogt.

00:20:35.572 --> 00:20:37.189
mir ze'mir gevezn in tsug,

00:20:38.129 --> 00:20:40.990
ze'mir geven in eyn vagon, zekhtsik mentshn,

00:20:42.398 --> 00:20:43.875
un,

00:20:44.195 --> 00:20:49.428
s'hot in gantsn gedoyert fir un tsvantsik sho umgefer biz m'iz ongekumen keyn BIRKENAU,

00:20:50.668 --> 00:20:52.143
unter vegs,

00:20:52.461 --> 00:20:54.491
hot a mentsh zikh gevolt,

00:20:54.516 --> 00:20:58.314
hot, nisht er hot gevolt, er iz aroysgeshprungen fun mitn tsug,

00:20:58.957 --> 00:21:02.933
un di soldatn hobn im glaykh geshosn, er iz dort geblibn toyt.

00:21:02.129 --> 00:21:03.566
du host es gezen.

00:21:03.589 --> 00:21:04.230
yo.

00:21:05.331 --> 00:21:11.214
gezen ho'mir nisht genoy, vayl der tsug iz vayter geforn, yo, mir ho'mir ober gevust vos, vos s'hot pasirt.

00:21:10.609 --> 00:21:11.726
du host gehert...

00:21:11.451 --> 00:21:16.678
yo, mir ho'mir gehert dem shos, nisht eyns, er hot bakumen merere koyln.

00:21:17.482 --> 00:21:22.267
un nokh dem ze'mir ongekumen keyn Birkenoy, s'iz geven shabes, mitog.

00:21:22.411 --> 00:21:24.005
vos hostu getrogt?

00:21:24.018 --> 00:21:25.732
ver, ikh?

00:21:24.824 --> 00:21:25.350
yo.

00:21:25.767 --> 00:21:28.823
ikh hob dir dokh gezogt vos ikh hob shoyn ongehat.

00:21:28.911 --> 00:21:31.000
zog mir vider.

00:22:00.763 --> 00:22:05.470
ikh hob ongehat a sheynem vinter-mantl nokh vayl s'iz geven kalt nokh demolts.

00:22:06.036 --> 00:22:08.056
mit a sheynem pelts-krogn.

00:22:08.927 --> 00:22:10.491
un a yidn-hut.

00:22:11.423 --> 00:22:14.512
mit a shirem oyf di hent. un a kleyn kufertl.

00:22:15.241 --> 00:22:18.262
dos hob ikh getrogn oyf Oyshvits.

00:22:44.705 --> 00:22:48.637
vos hot pasirt ven du host aropgeganen fun di vagon?

00:22:48.806 --> 00:22:52.068
un mir ze'mir aropgegangen fun di vagon,

00:22:53.465 --> 00:22:58.517
hobn mir zikh gemuzt shteln in di reye, finef mentshn,

00:22:58.586 --> 00:23:01.879
imer finef mentshn tsuzamen mit di hent,

00:23:02.241 --> 00:23:08.051
dem Koleshitser rebn hobn mir genumen in der mit, un tsvey zenen mir gevezn ekstre.

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:13.275
er hot nokh a freg getun, "nu, vi ze ikh oys? vel ikh durkhkumen?"

00:23:13.275 --> 00:23:15.482
dos hot er gefregt mit dey verter.

00:23:16.448 --> 00:23:20.724
un, dan iz gekumen di SELEKTION, fun Mengelen.

00:23:20.775 --> 00:23:22.155
du host gezen Mengele?

00:23:22.164 --> 00:23:22.827
yo.

00:23:22.844 --> 00:23:25.591
vi azoy hot er gekukt? vi azoy hot er...

00:23:24.486 --> 00:23:29.637
an ofitsir ongetun, azoy vi ale daytshe ofitsirn.

00:23:30.431 --> 00:23:35.045
un dan hot er gemakht mit di finger far Koleshitser rebn er zol aroyskumen.

00:23:35.045 --> 00:23:37.758
un er hot im geshikt oyf di andere zayt.

00:23:38.438 --> 00:23:43.212
dort vu me hot di mentshn getrogn tsu gaz-kamer.

00:23:44.362 --> 00:23:49.224
undz hot men genemen in a bod.

00:23:49.224 --> 00:23:52.534
me hot undz ale gelozt oystun gants naket.

00:23:52.903 --> 00:23:55.103
un me hot undz arayngefirt in bod.

00:23:55.879 --> 00:24:01.877
un dan nokh dem hot men undz ongetun mit geshtrayfte kleyder, un yeder hot gehat a a numer.

00:24:01.970 --> 00:24:03.206
oyfn kleyd.

00:24:05.673 --> 00:24:08.982
un dan hot men undz arayngefirt in di barakn.

00:24:09.775 --> 00:24:12.465
ze'mir dort gevezn dray tog.

00:24:14.120 --> 00:24:15.827
dray tog.

00:24:15.973 --> 00:24:20.206
nokh di dray tog hot men undz gefirt dan in arbayts-lager.

00:24:20.356 --> 00:24:27.241
ven du host nokh gevezn in BIRKENAU, vi azoy... du host gehat esn?

00:24:27.170 --> 00:24:30.689
zey hobn gegebn, zey hobn dort gegebn broyt. ikh,

00:24:30.762 --> 00:24:35.034
ikh hob es nisht a mol nokh gekent esn, dos broyne broyt vos zey hobn gegesn.

00:24:35.431 --> 00:24:38.241
hob ikh dortn gelozt, kh'hob es nisht a mol gegesn.

00:24:37.060 --> 00:24:40.517
far vos hostu nisht gekent es esn?

00:24:40.536 --> 00:24:45.615
kh'hob nisht gehat dos gefil dos tsu esn nokh demolts, deys broyt dortn.

00:24:45.455 --> 00:24:48.793
zey hobn dir gegebn a zup, tsi epes tsu trinken?

00:24:47.888 --> 00:24:51.585
yo, zey hobn gegen a zup, un zey hobn gegebn broyt.

00:24:51.379 --> 00:24:54.534
un vifl mener hobn gevezn in di barok?

00:24:54.620 --> 00:25:00.120
dos veys ikh nisht, ken ikh dir nisht zogn, ober a sakh mentshn. a por hundert. s'iz geven groyse barakn.

00:25:00.189 --> 00:25:02.756
un vu hostu geshlofn in di barakn?

00:25:02.011 --> 00:25:07.178
yo, dort iz shoyn gevezn, in di barak iz gevezn azelkhe gelegers, PRITSCHEN, JA?

00:25:07.325 --> 00:25:09.775
vu me hot zikh gekent leygn shlofn.

00:25:10.448 --> 00:25:13.810
s'gevezn dray shtok, dakht zikh mir.

00:25:14.546 --> 00:25:21.620
AND ven du host avekgeganen fun BIRKENAU, in velkhe lager hobn zey dir gebrengt?

00:25:21.679 --> 00:25:28.245
fun Birkenoy s-, hot men undz avekgefirt keyn OBERWÜSTEGIERSDORF, dos iz in Shlezyen.

00:25:28.533 --> 00:25:29.404
ye?

00:25:29.547 --> 00:25:35.903
dort ze'mir ongekumen, fuftsn hundert mentshn. vu, vos mit di andere iz pasirt veys ikh nisht.

00:25:37.294 --> 00:25:40.384
alzo fuftsn hundert mentshn ze'mir dort ongekumen,

00:25:40.400 --> 00:25:44.015
zey hobn gevezn HUNGarishe mentshn tsi andere mentshn?

00:25:43.298 --> 00:25:47.702
s'iz, neyn, s'iz gevezn tsvishn undz shoyn dray hundert poylishe yidelekh oykh.

00:25:47.716 --> 00:25:49.543
SO zey hobn arayngemisht...

00:25:48.913 --> 00:25:51.473
arayngemisht poylishe yinglekh oykh.

00:25:51.581 --> 00:25:56.000
AND vi lang hostu geblayb- geblibn in dem lager?

00:25:56.019 --> 00:25:58.982
in dem lager bin ikh gevezn

00:26:00.308 --> 00:26:02.524
biz mite zumer.

00:26:02.740 --> 00:26:07.169
du gedenkst di nomen fun di komendant fun dem lager?

00:26:06.144 --> 00:26:06.666
yo.

00:26:06.907 --> 00:26:10.386
der nomen fun komendant hot geheysn LÜTKEMEYER.

00:26:11.279 --> 00:26:13.341
geven a groyser roshe.

00:26:14.422 --> 00:26:17.552
un azoy vi ikh bin ongekumen in dem lager,

00:26:18.201 --> 00:26:21.904
hob ikh gearbet tsu ersht in a

00:26:22.044 --> 00:26:23.773
kleyne komando,

00:26:24.193 --> 00:26:29.265
vos me hot gemakht di vaser-leytungen in dem dorf,

00:26:29.265 --> 00:26:32.399
un undz ho'mir gemakht di griber, yo?

00:26:32.475 --> 00:26:37.843
undz ze'mir gevezn dortn draytsn mentshn, in dey komando.

00:26:38.871 --> 00:26:43.000
iz gevezn dort zeyer a f- voyle poylishe goyte

00:26:44.472 --> 00:26:48.654
vos zi hot undz yedn tog geleygt draytsn pekelekh,

00:26:49.512 --> 00:26:53.028
far undz, far yedn eynem a pekele,

00:26:53.104 --> 00:26:56.229
baym STRASSENRAND azoy vi undz ze'mir gegangen,

00:26:56.276 --> 00:26:59.611
in yedn pekele iz geven tsvey reftelekh broyt.

00:27:00.166 --> 00:27:03.127
tsvey tsigaretlekh, un an epl.

00:27:03.465 --> 00:27:05.813
dos hot zi undz geleygt yedn tog,

00:27:05.813 --> 00:27:08.716
dey poylishe goyte. zeyer a voyle goyte geven.

00:27:09.007 --> 00:27:11.485
du gedenkst di nomen fun dem mentsh?

00:27:11.502 --> 00:27:16.809
neyn. kh'hob nisht, keyn mol nisht gevust dem nomen fun di goyte, me hot dokh nisht getort redn mit ir, m'hot...

00:27:16.809 --> 00:27:19.825
zi hot dos geleygt in STRASSENRAND me zol nisht zen.

00:27:20.181 --> 00:27:24.655
zi hot zikh aleyn dos lebn ayngeshtelt oyf dem.

00:27:28.668 --> 00:27:32.318
iz geven zeyer a voyle goyte. ikh vel nokh dertseyln fun dey goyte.

00:27:32.377 --> 00:27:34.386
gezogt hot zi,

00:27:35.922 --> 00:27:40.659
vayl, ven me hot gearbet nebn ir hoyz, di grobung, hot men

00:27:40.746 --> 00:27:46.447
hot men gelozt arayngeyn tsu yedn hoyz nemen vasers mitog, vayl s'iz geven varem, s'iz shoyn geven zumer,

00:27:46.552 --> 00:27:48.193
tsum trinken, yo?

00:27:48.228 --> 00:27:50.938
ven m'iz tsu ir gekumen, bay ir hoyz,

00:27:51.000 --> 00:27:58.946
hot zi undz gegebn, mit a eymer ze'mir gegangen nokh vaser, hot undz, hot zi undz gegebn anshtot vaser an eymer KAFFEE.

00:28:00.219 --> 00:28:04.010
mir zol'mir trinken KAFFEE dortn, un demolts hot zi gezogt oykh,

00:28:04.120 --> 00:28:06.342
"ikh hof az, az

00:28:06.462 --> 00:28:09.581
az mayn zun vos er iz a soldat,

00:28:10.778 --> 00:28:15.247
az er vet oykh bakumen GESCHENKE fun fremde mentshn".

00:28:16.033 --> 00:28:16.912
O.K.

00:28:19.035 --> 00:28:19.724
ye.